{
  "video_id": "5Knz100ldLM",
  "title": "Dave Meslin: The antidote to apathy",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15894.0,
      "end_time": 19363.0,
      "text": "How often do we hear that people just don&#39;t care?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 20218.0,
      "end_time": 21809.0,
      "text": "How many times have you been told"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21833.0,
      "end_time": 25730.0,
      "text": "that real, substantial change isn&#39;t possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25980.0,
      "end_time": 27173.0,
      "text": "because most people are too selfish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27197.0,
      "end_time": 29128.0,
      "text": "too stupid or too lazy"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29153.0,
      "end_time": 31785.0,
      "text": "to try to make a difference in their community?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31809.0,
      "end_time": 34903.0,
      "text": "I propose to you today that apathy as we think we know it"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34927.0,
      "end_time": 36638.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t actually exist;"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36662.0,
      "end_time": 38836.0,
      "text": "but rather, that people do care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38860.0,
      "end_time": 42569.0,
      "text": "but that we live in a world that actively discourages engagement"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42593.0,
      "end_time": 45954.0,
      "text": "by constantly putting obstacles and barriers in our way."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45978.0,
      "end_time": 48100.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll give you some examples of what I mean."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48340.0,
      "end_time": 49747.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s start with city hall."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50123.0,
      "end_time": 51836.0,
      "text": "You ever see one of these before?"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 52218.0,
      "end_time": 53836.0,
      "text": "This is a newspaper ad."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53860.0,
      "end_time": 57228.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a notice of a zoning application change for a new office building"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57252.0,
      "end_time": 59323.0,
      "text": "so the neighborhood knows what&#39;s happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59347.0,
      "end_time": 61269.0,
      "text": "As you can see, it&#39;s impossible to read."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61293.0,
      "end_time": 62669.0,
      "text": "You need to get halfway down"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 62693.0,
      "end_time": 65227.0,
      "text": "to even find out which address they&#39;re talking about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65251.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67395.0,
      "text": "and then further down, in tiny 10-point font,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67419.0,
      "end_time": 69455.0,
      "text": "to find out how to actually get involved."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 69479.0,
      "end_time": 72606.0,
      "text": "Imagine if the private sector advertised in the same way --"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72630.0,
      "end_time": 74672.0,
      "text": "if Nike wanted to sell a pair of shoes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 74696.0,
      "end_time": 75836.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75860.0,
      "end_time": 77825.0,
      "text": "And put an ad in the paper like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 77849.0,
      "end_time": 81836.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81860.0,
      "end_time": 83836.0,
      "text": "Now, that would never happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 84695.0,
      "end_time": 86273.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ll never see an ad like that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 86298.0,
      "end_time": 88729.0,
      "text": "because Nike actually wants you to buy their shoes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 88753.0,
      "end_time": 91634.0,
      "text": "whereas the city of Toronto clearly doesn&#39;t want you involved"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 91658.0,
      "end_time": 92910.0,
      "text": "with the planning process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 92934.0,
      "end_time": 95350.0,
      "text": "otherwise their ads would look something like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 95374.0,
      "end_time": 97390.0,
      "text": "with all the information laid out clearly."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 97415.0,
      "end_time": 99832.0,
      "text": "As long as the city&#39;s putting out notices like this"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 99856.0,
      "end_time": 101282.0,
      "text": "to try to get people engaged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 101306.0,
      "end_time": 103640.0,
      "text": "then of course people aren&#39;t going to be engaged."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 103664.0,
      "end_time": 106252.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s not apathy; that&#39;s intentional exclusion."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 107584.0,
      "end_time": 108848.0,
      "text": "Public space."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 108872.0,
      "end_time": 111660.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 111781.0,
      "end_time": 114116.0,
      "text": "The manner in which we mistreat our public spaces"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 114140.0,
      "end_time": 118400.0,
      "text": "is a huge obstacle towards any type of progressive political change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 118424.0,
      "end_time": 121623.0,
      "text": "because we&#39;ve essentially put a price tag on freedom of expression."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 121647.0,
      "end_time": 124232.0,
      "text": "Whoever has the most money gets the loudest voice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 124256.0,
      "end_time": 126655.0,
      "text": "dominating the visual and mental environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 126679.0,
      "end_time": 129658.0,
      "text": "The problem with this model is there are some amazing messages"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 129683.0,
      "end_time": 132524.0,
      "text": "that need to be said, that aren&#39;t profitable to say."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 132548.0,
      "end_time": 135500.0,
      "text": "So you&#39;re never going to see them on a billboard."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 136150.0,
      "end_time": 137628.0,
      "text": "The media plays an important role"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 137652.0,
      "end_time": 140835.0,
      "text": "in developing our relationship with political change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 140860.0,
      "end_time": 145110.0,
      "text": "mainly by ignoring politics and focusing on celebrities and scandals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 145350.0,
      "end_time": 147888.0,
      "text": "but even when they do talk about important political issues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 147912.0,
      "end_time": 150765.0,
      "text": "they do it in a way that I feel discourages engagement."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 150789.0,
      "end_time": 152600.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll give you an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 152310.0,
      "end_time": 155624.0,
      "text": "The \"Now\" magazine from last week: progressive, downtown weekly in Toronto."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 155648.0,
      "end_time": 156835.0,
      "text": "This is the cover story."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 156860.0,
      "end_time": 159348.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an article about a theater performance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 159372.0,
      "end_time": 162130.0,
      "text": "and it starts with basic information about where it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 162154.0,
      "end_time": 165679.0,
      "text": "in case you actually want to go and see it after you&#39;ve read the article --"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 165703.0,
      "end_time": 167486.0,
      "text": "where, the time, the website."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 167510.0,
      "end_time": 169915.0,
      "text": "Same with this -- it&#39;s a movie review."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 169939.0,
      "end_time": 171523.0,
      "text": "An art review."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 171547.0,
      "end_time": 174685.0,
      "text": "A book review -- where the reading is in case you want to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 174709.0,
      "end_time": 177419.0,
      "text": "A restaurant -- you might not want to just read about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 177443.0,
      "end_time": 178870.0,
      "text": "maybe you want to go there."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 178894.0,
      "end_time": 182667.0,
      "text": "So they tell you where it is, the prices, the address, the phone number, etc."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 182691.0,
      "end_time": 184668.0,
      "text": "Then you get to their political articles."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 184692.0,
      "end_time": 188152.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a great article about an important election race that&#39;s happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 188176.0,
      "end_time": 190505.0,
      "text": "It talks about the candidates, written very well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 190529.0,
      "end_time": 193756.0,
      "text": "but no information, no follow-up, no websites for the campaigns,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 193780.0,
      "end_time": 197305.0,
      "text": "no information about when the debates are, where the campaign offices are."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 197329.0,
      "end_time": 198758.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s another good article,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 198782.0,
      "end_time": 201836.0,
      "text": "about a new campaign opposing privatization of transit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 201860.0,
      "end_time": 204574.0,
      "text": "without any contact information for the campaign."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 204598.0,
      "end_time": 206122.0,
      "text": "The message seems to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 206146.0,
      "end_time": 209557.0,
      "text": "that the readers are most likely to want to eat, maybe read a book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 209581.0,
      "end_time": 212344.0,
      "text": "maybe see a movie, but not be engaged in their community."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 212368.0,
      "end_time": 215506.0,
      "text": "You might think this is a small thing, but I think it&#39;s important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 215530.0,
      "end_time": 216926.0,
      "text": "because it sets a tone"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 216950.0,
      "end_time": 222578.0,
      "text": "and it reinforces the dangerous idea that politics is a spectator sport."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 223423.0,
      "end_time": 225668.0,
      "text": "Heroes: How do we view leadership?"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 225692.0,
      "end_time": 228355.0,
      "text": "Look at these 10 movies. What do they have in common?"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 228379.0,
      "end_time": 229543.0,
      "text": "Anyone?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 231298.0,
      "end_time": 233372.0,
      "text": "They all have heroes who were chosen."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 233396.0,
      "end_time": 236111.0,
      "text": "Someone came up to them and said, \"You&#39;re the chosen one."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 236135.0,
      "end_time": 238409.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a prophecy. You have to save the world.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 238433.0,
      "end_time": 241734.0,
      "text": "And then they go off and save the world because they&#39;ve been told to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 241759.0,
      "end_time": 243317.0,
      "text": "with a few people tagging along."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 243342.0,
      "end_time": 244498.0,
      "text": "This helps me understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 244522.0,
      "end_time": 247548.0,
      "text": "why a lot of people have trouble seeing themselves as leaders --"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 247573.0,
      "end_time": 251970.0,
      "text": "because it sends all the wrong messages about what leadership is about."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 251121.0,
      "end_time": 253634.0,
      "text": "A heroic effort is a collective effort,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 253658.0,
      "end_time": 254835.0,
      "text": "number one."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 255188.0,
      "end_time": 258555.0,
      "text": "Number two, it&#39;s imperfect; it&#39;s not very glamorous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 258579.0,
      "end_time": 260762.0,
      "text": "and doesn&#39;t suddenly start and suddenly end."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 260786.0,
      "end_time": 262848.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an ongoing process your whole life."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 262872.0,
      "end_time": 264649.0,
      "text": "But most importantly, it&#39;s voluntary."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 264673.0,
      "end_time": 266910.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s voluntary."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 266115.0,
      "end_time": 268478.0,
      "text": "As long as we&#39;re teaching our kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 268502.0,
      "end_time": 271924.0,
      "text": "that heroism starts when someone scratches a mark on your forehead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 271948.0,
      "end_time": 274174.0,
      "text": "or someone tells you you&#39;re part of a prophecy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 274198.0,
      "end_time": 277227.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re missing the most important characteristic of leadership,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 277251.0,
      "end_time": 278938.0,
      "text": "which is that it comes from within."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 278962.0,
      "end_time": 282836.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about following your own dreams, uninvited,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 282860.0,
      "end_time": 285836.0,
      "text": "and then working with others to make those dreams come true."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 285860.0,
      "end_time": 287836.0,
      "text": "Political parties: oh, boy."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 288259.0,
      "end_time": 292752.0,
      "text": "Political parties could and should be one of the basic entry points"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 292776.0,
      "end_time": 294703.0,
      "text": "for people to get engaged in politics."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 294727.0,
      "end_time": 296991.0,
      "text": "Instead, they&#39;ve become, sadly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 297160.0,
      "end_time": 299902.0,
      "text": "uninspiring and uncreative organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 299926.0,
      "end_time": 303836.0,
      "text": "that rely so heavily on market research and polling and focus groups"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 303860.0,
      "end_time": 305908.0,
      "text": "that they end up all saying the same thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 305932.0,
      "end_time": 309280.0,
      "text": "pretty much regurgitating back to us what we already want to hear"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 309520.0,
      "end_time": 311836.0,
      "text": "at the expense of putting forward bold and creative ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 311860.0,
      "end_time": 314616.0,
      "text": "And people can smell that, and it feeds cynicism."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 314640.0,
      "end_time": 320616.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 320984.0,
      "end_time": 322428.0,
      "text": "Charitable status."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 322452.0,
      "end_time": 326206.0,
      "text": "Groups who have charitable status in Canada aren&#39;t allowed to do advocacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 326230.0,
      "end_time": 328761.0,
      "text": "This is a huge problem and a huge obstacle to change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 328785.0,
      "end_time": 332257.0,
      "text": "because it means that some of the most passionate and informed voices"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 332281.0,
      "end_time": 335164.0,
      "text": "are completely silenced, especially during election time."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 335188.0,
      "end_time": 338551.0,
      "text": "Which leads us to the last one, which is: our elections."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 338956.0,
      "end_time": 340124.0,
      "text": "As you may have noticed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 340148.0,
      "end_time": 342255.0,
      "text": "our elections in Canada are a complete joke."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 342279.0,
      "end_time": 343770.0,
      "text": "We use out-of-date systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 343794.0,
      "end_time": 346940.0,
      "text": "that are unfair and create random results."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 346119.0,
      "end_time": 347836.0,
      "text": "Canada&#39;s currently led by a party"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 347860.0,
      "end_time": 350308.0,
      "text": "that most Canadians didn&#39;t actually want."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 350332.0,
      "end_time": 353947.0,
      "text": "How can we honestly and genuinely encourage more people to vote"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 353971.0,
      "end_time": 356248.0,
      "text": "when votes don&#39;t count in Canada?"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 356272.0,
      "end_time": 359640.0,
      "text": "You add all this up together, and of course people are apathetic."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 359664.0,
      "end_time": 361724.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like trying to run into a brick wall."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 361748.0,
      "end_time": 365650.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;m not trying to be negative by throwing all these obstacles out"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 365890.0,
      "end_time": 366689.0,
      "text": "and explaining what&#39;s in our way."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 366713.0,
      "end_time": 367866.0,
      "text": "Quite the opposite --"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 367890.0,
      "end_time": 372373.0,
      "text": "I actually think people are amazing and smart and that they do care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 372477.0,
      "end_time": 374835.0,
      "text": "but that, as I said, we live in this environment"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 374860.0,
      "end_time": 377998.0,
      "text": "where all these obstacles are being put in our way."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 378748.0,
      "end_time": 382199.0,
      "text": "As long as we believe that people, our own neighbors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 382223.0,
      "end_time": 384919.0,
      "text": "are selfish, stupid or lazy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 385677.0,
      "end_time": 386969.0,
      "text": "then there&#39;s no hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 388640.0,
      "end_time": 390375.0,
      "text": "But we can change all those things I mentioned."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 390399.0,
      "end_time": 391836.0,
      "text": "We can open up city hall."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 391860.0,
      "end_time": 393592.0,
      "text": "We can reform our electoral systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 393616.0,
      "end_time": 395592.0,
      "text": "We can democratize our public spaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 395617.0,
      "end_time": 397389.0,
      "text": "My main message is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 397413.0,
      "end_time": 399910.0,
      "text": "if we can redefine apathy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 399115.0,
      "end_time": 401137.0,
      "text": "not as some kind of internal syndrome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 401161.0,
      "end_time": 405955.0,
      "text": "but as a complex web of cultural barriers that reinforces disengagement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 406589.0,
      "end_time": 412152.0,
      "text": "and if we can clearly define, clearly identify what those obstacles are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 412176.0,
      "end_time": 415767.0,
      "text": "and then if we can work together collectively to dismantle those obstacles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 415791.0,
      "end_time": 417450.0,
      "text": "then anything is possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 417690.0,
      "end_time": 418229.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 418253.0,
      "end_time": 420253.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}